{"tid":2146523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那：創紀錄！上半年5816人放棄美國國籍","createTime":"2020-08-08T15:37:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T04:00:12.000Z","uid":136415,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"0d79446751337b9e1b0ac66d75ef745cc18c1001","tid":2146523,"uid":136415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T15:37:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【創紀錄！#上半年5816人放棄美國國籍# 】據美通社（PR Newswire）6日消息，紐約班布里奇會計師事務所一項研究報告顯示，2020年的前6個月，放棄美國國籍的美國人數達到創紀錄水平，為5816人。根據美國國家稅務局條例，政府每3個月公佈一次所有放棄公民身份的美國人姓名。今年的前6個月有5816名美國人放棄國籍，這遠遠超過了2019年4個季度的總數（2072人）。<br />\n    越來越多的美國僑民放棄國籍是由於當前的疫情讓他們有時間重新審視自己與美國的關係，而且認為當前的政治氣候以及美國的年度稅務申報讓人難以忍受。「這些生活在國外的美國公民，他們仍需要每年在美國提交納稅申報表，繳納潛在的稅款以及報告他們所有的外國銀行賬戶、投資以及養老金情況&hellip;&hellip;」紐約班布里奇會計師事務所的合伙人班布里奇說，「他們這才採取了放棄國籍的嚴肅做法，因為他們並不打算回美國生活。」（環球網，YX）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://world.huanqiu.com/article/3zNp7mdM8EW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fworld.huanqiu.com%2Farticle%2F3zNp7mdM8EW&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiWyKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=c4f258e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://world.huanqiu.com/article/3zNp7mdM8EW</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QeAdDz4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQeAdDz4.png&h=396b5253&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5186349204c6bc4bc6db086ddd48a1cecc3aa18a","tid":2146523,"uid":274094,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"0d79446751337b9e1b0ac66d75ef745cc18c1001","tid":2146523,"uid":136415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"re